Coverage


November  2, 2011
Progress To Settle With CVO Holders Over $42M Loss
Progress Energy Inc. struck a settlement Wednesday to end a lawsuit alleging it stiffed holders of its contingent value obligations some $42 million by adopting an improper tax position in 2005 in violation of an agreement related to an earlier merger.


